column54: It is the capital planet for the [[Alliance of Galactic Travellers]] in the [[Yihelli Quadrant]] region of the [[Euclid]] [[Galaxy]]. The planet serves as the hub of activity for the AGT in [[Euclid]]. In AGT Lore is the physical location of the [[AGT Galactic Archives]] Interface and meeting location for the [[AGT Senior Leadership Team]].
column55: The AGT Embassy is located around Embassy Lake. There are many bases located around this lake. The main embassy being prominent in the center. Directly above the Embassy at the cloud level of the atmosphere is a Skybase.

column54: It has significance, as this planet represents the point of entry into the [[Yihelli Quadrant]] by the [[Alliance of Galactic Travellers]]. This took place at the end of the [[Atlas Rises]] era when the PS4 based AGT were actively seeking to relocate their primary civilised space presence within the Euclid galaxy and had reached agreement with the [[Galactic Hub Project]] to migrate the civilisation's capital region to within a convenient distance of that civilisation.
It is a [[Red Force]] planet stronghold with production starting in late 2018.
